  <Summary>The Chameleon tricks the Hulk into breaking his friend out of jail.

The Tomorrow Man asks Iron Man and Spider-Man to help him against a mutual enemy, but he plans on using that help to weaken and conquer Kang.

With the Avengers captured, Spider-Man must turn to the Human Torch to help him track down the Tomorrow Man's time bombs.

Spider-Man enlists the Inhumans to help him get back to the 23rd century to rescue the Avengers.</Summary>
